    <title>Prime Day is a great time to get the Galaxy Watch 6 Classic for 33 percent off</title>
    <content type="html">  

    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img alt="Close up of Galaxy Watch 6 Classic" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/iKgcTOsPWmwK24snYAv6V7u3izw=/0x0:2550x1700/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73639462/236731_Samsung_Galaxy_Watch_6_AKrales_0187.0.jpg" /&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;em&gt;Get that physical rotating bezel!&lt;/em&gt; | Photo by Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption&gt;
    &lt;/figure&gt;

  &lt;p id="ooHTHt"&gt;This year’s Samsung Galaxy Watch lineup had no physical rotating bezels. Boo. So, it’s a good thing that &lt;a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C791819Q?th=1&amp;amp;tag=theverge02-20" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;the Galaxy Watch 6 Classic&lt;/a&gt; is roughly 33 percent off for Amazon Prime Day. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p id="ecKcon"&gt;This might be the last-gen Galaxy Watch, but hardware-wise, you’re not missing out on much besides a slightly faster processor and a new 3-in-1 BioActive sensor. (That said, Samsung doesn’t make much use of the new sensor yet outside an experimental new Advanced Glycation End Products metric.) The &lt;a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C79918S5?th=1&amp;amp;tag=theverge02-20" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;43mm Bluetooth version&lt;/a&gt; is $269.93, while the &lt;a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C79918S5?th=1&amp;amp;tag=theverge02-20" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;larger 47mm&lt;/a&gt; is $281.99. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div id="Ea7Bkx"&gt;&lt;div data-anthem-component="productcard:12447360"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p id="JUQBX2"&gt;Personally, this is the Galaxy Watch I’d pick for myself. While I like the newest Galaxy Watch 7 (which is &lt;a href="https://www.amazon.com/SAMSUNG-Bluetooth-Smartwatch-Wellness-Manufacturer/dp/B0D1YQKDML?dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.Wtja_lA_fCM5S0rLBagDTq7LmL_5vLXdlz3EbzHpJm-Sxmezp7fBZDeKFJ8oCmhC4kgdAZpLtyh-TLUZZnbpwbzUvU_dKs6tMxbiG3UvyhP9qpdTSKa4FCYm66IOV2Md7vchyr3oousFuMzrR5TC0AJuz1yEzo3Kxq89L7yd5kQLX1jUnCn4cc3g1KrDZMh6F36YN9zWIVtT6KEi0cjXrKqeOf9CiiqZGxdOFvrJLNw.1WW4Dwdoapw3JhIg6qgkBvfKspsngly8T1gGl3Dh39M&amp;amp;dib_tag=se&amp;amp;keywords=samsung+galaxy+watch&amp;amp;psr=PDAY&amp;amp;qid=1728391763&amp;amp;s=pbdd&amp;amp;sr=1-4&amp;amp;ufe=INHOUSE_INSTALLMENTS%3AUS_5M_VENDOR_FUNDING&amp;amp;th=1&amp;amp;tag=theverge02-20" rel="sponsored nofollow noopener" target="_blank"&gt;also on sale for $261&lt;/a&gt;), I found myself missing the Classic’s rotating bezel. &lt;/p&gt;
